---
// about.astro - Aboutページ + 免責事項
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="About Boot Craft Archive — the definitive database of crafted leather boots and shoes for enthusiasts worldwide."
>
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-header__title">About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="article-layout">
      <h2>Boot Craft Archive</h2>
      <p>
        Boot Craft Archive is the definitive online database for quality leather boots and shoes.
        We catalog and review footwear from the world's finest bootmakers — from the heritage
        workshops of Red Wing and Wolverine in America to the legendary factories of Tricker's
        and Crockett & Jones in Northampton, England.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our mission is to help boot enthusiasts, style-conscious professionals, and newcomers
        alike find the perfect pair of welted footwear. We provide detailed specifications, leather
        and construction comparisons, and honest reviews based on real-world usage.
      </p>

      <h2>What Makes Us Different</h2>
      <p>
        Unlike generic review sites, we specialize exclusively in quality crafted footwear. Our
        leather database with radar charts helps you understand exactly what each leather offers.
        Our construction guide explains the engineering behind every welt type. And our comparison
        tool lets you put any two boots side by side.
      </p>

      <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
      <p>
        Boot Craft Archive is a participant in affiliate programs including Amazon Associates.
        This means we may earn a small commission when you purchase through our links, at no
        additional cost to you. This helps us maintain and improve this resource.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our reviews and recommendations are independent. Affiliate relationships never influence
        our ratings or which boots we recommend.
      </p>

      <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>
        The information provided on Boot Craft Archive is for general informational purposes
        only. While we strive for accuracy, prices, availability, and specifications may change
        without notice. We are not responsible for any purchasing decisions made based on our content.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions, corrections, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.
        <br />Email: info@bootcraftarchive.com
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
